-- India's state-run banks to tap markets "very soon" -govt official
-- By Rajesh Kumar Singh
-- Tue Sep 30, 2014 01:40AM EDT
-- None



NEW DELHI, Sept 30 (Reuters) - India's state-run banks will "very soon" start raising funds from markets, Financial Services Secretary G.S. Sandhu said on Tuesday, as part of government's efforts to infuse capital into banks.

